overview: Three hours with beautiful and sexy Russian Boys.  Dolphin Entertainment proudly presents Russian Beauty Vol. 2: Oleg. This film is about superstar Oleg Vorobyev - one of Dolphin's first exclusive models - and how he began his career with Dolphin Entertainment as an innocent boy and grew into being a man. Each scene features a commentary by Oleg and director Alex Clark.  It's thrilling to watch Oleg go down the memory lane, talking about his favorite partners as well as the most exciting (and worst) moments of his adult career. He has been featured in many magazines, and his films have sold thousands of copies worldwide.  Cast: Anatoliy, Cody Flash, Dan Te, Edan, Evgeniy W., Lex,Max, Pasha, Tomas, Tommy Hansen
title: Russian Beauty 3: Edan
